commands: execute as @s unless score @s satsu.iron.man.choose_armor.test matches 0.. run scoreboard players set @s satsu.iron.man.choose_armor.test 2

choose.armor.set.title: set
commands: execute as @s run scoreboard players operation @s satsu.iron.man.armor = @s satsu.iron.man.choose_armor
execute as @s[scores={satsu.iron.man.choose_armor=1}] unless score @s satsu.iron.man.mask matches 0.. run scoreboard players set @s satsu.iron.man.mask 0
